  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Sales Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>Sales and Business Development:</strong>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Identify and develop new business opportunities and markets.</li>\n      <li>Understand client needs and recommend suitable products or services.</li>\n      <li>Prepare proposals and quotations.</li>\n      <li>Conduct presentations of the product offered to customers.</li>\n      <li>Address clients query and concerns and provide valuable solutions that meet customer needs.</li>\n      <li>Close sales by building rapport with customers, explaining product and service capabilities, and overcoming objections.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong>Product Knowledge:</strong>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Continuous learning of the company’s offered products and services.</li>\n      <li>Stay updated on industry trends, competitor products, and technological advancements.</li>\n      <li>Analyze competitors’ products and strategies to identify areas for differentiation.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong>Relationship Management:</strong>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Build and maintain strong, long-lasting customer relationships.</li>\n      <li>Act as a trusted advisor to clients, understanding their business/plant needs       and challenges.</li>\n      <li>Collaborate with the sales, operations, and customer service teams to ensure customer       satisfaction.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required as training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Goal driven and result-oriented</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and likeable personality.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in MS officetation skills</li>\n  <li>Proficiency       in MS office</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li>\n</ul>",
